OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780150315
OL,3,CTeenage girl who was pulled from water
OL,4,Cover bank holiday dies
OL,6,FA teenage girl has died after getting
OL,7,Finto difficulty while swimming on a
OL,8,Fbeach in Merseyside.
OL,10,FChiedza Nyanjowa was swimming on
OL,11,FFormby Beach on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,12,FEmergency Services were called to the
OL,13,Fbeach on Albert Road after concerns
OL,14,Fwere raised for her safety.
OL,16,FThe 15-year-old from Cheshire was
OL,17,Fairlifted to Alder Hey Children's
OL,18,FHospital, where she passed away on
OL,19,FSaturday 30 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
