OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780150315
OL,3,CTeenage girl who was pulled from water
OL,4,Cover bank holiday dies
OL,6,FChiedza's family has thanked the
OL,7,Fmembers of the public who pulled her
OL,8,Ffrom the water, along with those who
OL,9,Fcalled for help.
OL,11,FThe statement said: "Her family would
OL,12,Flike to express their gratitude to
OL,13,Feveryone that helped Chiedza. Her
OL,14,Ffamily are glad that there were people
OL,15,Faround her to support her, their
OL,16,Fsupport shows that she was loved.
OL,18,F"This is a difficult time for the
OL,19,Ffamily, who would appreciate any form
OL,20,Fof prayer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
