OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780150315
OL,3,CTeenage girl who was pulled from water
OL,4,Cover bank holiday dies
OL,6,F"Her family describe her as a bubbly
OL,7,Fperson, she loved Christ and going to
OL,8,Fchurch. She loved cooking, she was a
OL,9,Fgiver and wanted to be nurse when she
OL,10,Fgrew up so she could give back.
OL,12,F"She will be greatly missed and
OL,13,Fremembered for her kind spirit."
OL,15,FChiedza is the third young person from
OL,16,Fthe North West to die after entering
OL,17,Fthe water in the space of a week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
