PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780150315
OL,3,CTeenage girl who was pulled from water
OL,4,Cover bank holiday dies
OL,6,F12-year old Junior Slater died on
OL,7,FTuesday 26 May after he was last seen
OL,8,Fswimming in the River Ribble in
OL,9,FLancashire.
OL,11,FJust a few hours later, 17 year old
OL,12,FDavid Tita Jr's body was pulled from
OL,13,FPickmere Lake in Cheshire.
OL,15,FThe spike in tragedies has prompted
OL,16,Femergency services and the Royal Life
OL,17,FSaving Society (RLSS) to reissue
OL,18,Furgent water safety warnings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
