OL,3,CTeenage girl who was pulled from water
OL,4,Cover bank holiday dies
OL,6,FExperts have reminded the public that
OL,7,Fdespite hot air temperatures, open
OL,8,Fwater in rivers and lakes remain
OL,9,Fdangerously cold, increasing the risk
OL,10,Fof cold water shock.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
